    "long_instructions": "##### **Teacher Note**: This is Lesson 6, Level 6 from the curriculum. This is a **Check-In** level, meaning it would be a great level to formatively assess students' progress.\r\n___\r\n\r\n### Check-In\r\nYour goal is to use loops to make all the sounds in the workspace play together in sync. When you're done, your timeline should look like the example below.\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/7b3089fd3a7cc114f629152ecb20da6c-image-1741020219686.png)\r\n",
